task.en: In this app, delete the texts. Move the image icon outside of the VStack and then remove the VStack. Keep the attributes of the image unchanged. Don't modify other parts of the code.

pre_command: osascript -e 'tell application "Xcode" to close windows' && rm -rf /Users/ec2-user/Documents/BenchmarkApp && cp -r /Users/ec2-user/Benchmark_Backup/BenchmarkApp /Users/ec2-user/Documents && cd /Users/ec2-user/Documents/BenchmarkApp && git checkout 5ba51e8 && open -a Xcode /Users/ec2-user/Documents/BenchmarkApp
grading_command: cat /Users/ec2-user/Documents/BenchmarkApp/BenchmarkApp/ContentView.swift | sed -e 's|//.*||' -e 's|/\*[^*]*\*+\([^/]*\*/\)| |g' -e 's|/\*.*||' -e 's|.*\*/||' | tr -d '\n' | tr -d ' ' | grep -q 'structContentView:View{varbody:someView{Image(systemName:"globe").imageScale(.large).foregroundStyle(.tint)}}' && echo "True" || echo "False"
